This is a great value and nice place to stay during your trip to Key West.	The location was good and the price reasonable for Key West.	I've been at all three of the Key West Marriott Hotels and this is my favorite for value and relaxation.	I stayed at the Casa Marina as well during my vacation and in terms of overall value, the Fairfield comes out top every time.	Overall, property was a great value for the price!	I can recommend staying here but remember it is pretty far from all the action in central Key West.	I was able to book last minute with them and it was worth the trip.